a sidebar.

288
00:17:04,284 --> 00:17:05,154
No.

289
00:17:05,198 --> 00:17:06,068
Sorry.

290
00:17:06,112 --> 00:17:07,417
There's nothing I can do.

291
00:17:07,461 --> 00:17:08,375
[SIGH]

292
00:17:10,246 --> 00:17:12,509
What now?

293
00:17:12,553 --> 00:17:13,684
Work hard.

294
00:17:13,728 --> 00:17:14,598
Pay your dues.

295
00:17:14,642 --> 00:17:16,165
And your time will come.

