417
00:23:12,391 --> 00:23:15,872
[TYPING]

418
00:23:22,923 --> 00:23:23,837
[YAWN]

419
00:23:28,319 --> 00:23:29,364
[CHIMING]

420
00:23:29,408 --> 00:23:31,061
COMPUTER: Click here. Click
here.

421
00:23:31,105 --> 00:23:31,932
Click here.

422
00:23:31,975 --> 00:23:35,414
