424
00:24:05,792 --> 00:24:08,403
DISPATCHER [ON RADIO]: Unit
29-31, confirm ATA at Pier 17.

425
00:24:12,015 --> 00:24:15,410
[SIRENS]

426
00:24:16,846 --> 00:24:18,544
Denise Wilcox with "The
Tribune."

427
00:24:18,587 --> 00:24:19,675
What's the victim's name?

428
00:24:19,719 --> 00:24:21,634
Ho, hold up.

429
00:24:21,677 --> 00:24:24,375
If you had clearance, you'd
know.

430
00:24:24,419 --> 00:24:27,161
Woods, Lorna Woods.

431
00:24:27,204 --> 00:24:30,686
[MUSIC PLAYING]

432
00:24:36,649 --> 00:24:40,130
[CHATTER ON POLICE RADIOS]

433
