hell

505
00:27:57,501 --> 00:27:59,155
and that she would spend years
in purgatory

506
00:27:59,199 --> 00:28:02,419
making up for the fact that
she'd raised a tramp.

507
00:28:02,463 --> 00:28:03,725
THERAPIST: How did that make you
feel?

508
00:28:03,769 --> 00:28:04,813
Oh, peachy.

509
00:28:04,857 --> 00:28:06,728
