516
00:28:26,617 --> 00:28:27,706
Yeah.

517
00:28:27,749 --> 00:28:29,751
My mother got her wish.

518
00:28:29,795 --> 00:28:32,014
THERAPIST: How so?

519
00:28:32,058 --> 00:28:35,191
