520
00:28:35,235 --> 00:28:39,979
Yeah, till he showed up at "The
Trib" two days ago.

521
00:28:40,022 --> 00:28:41,328
Hm.

522
00:28:41,371 --> 00:28:44,548
I love sex, right?

523
00:28:44,592 --> 00:28:45,636
That's why I live with a lizard.

524
00:28:48,552 --> 00:28:51,294
So you never told Simon what
happened.

525
00:28:51,338 --> 00:28:52,252
No.

526
00:28:54,950 --> 00:28:56,822
THERAPIST: He must have wondered
why you suddenly left.

527
00:29:00,129 --> 00:29:02,784
Well, I was in Cliffcrest for a
year and a half.

528
00:29:02,828 --> 00:29:07,876
And when I got out, he had
graduated and moved away.

529
00:29:07,920 --> 00:29:09,530
THERAPIST: What was Cliffcrest
like?

530
00:29:09,573 --> 00:29:10,923
[FOREBODING MUSIC PLAYING]

531
00:29:10,966 --> 00:29:13,403
[LAUGHTER]

532
00:29:14,840 --> 00:29:18,104
I don't remember.

533
00:29:18,147 --> 00:29:20,062
You've-- you've blocked it out.

534
00:29:20,106 --> 00:29:21,890
I prefer to call it moving on.

535
00:29:21,934 --> 00:29:24,023
You treat yourself so hard,
