00:44:12,650 --> 00:44:14,042
That shouldn't be happening. - I
know, I know.

803
00:44:14,086 --> 00:44:14,956
Forget it. Forget it.

804
00:44:15,000 --> 00:44:15,827
[SIGH]

805
00:44:15,870 --> 00:44:16,915
[TYPING]

806
00:44:16,958 --> 00:44:17,916
[CHIMING]

807
00:44:17,959 --> 00:44:21,441
[MUSIC PLAYING]

808
00:44:23,008 --> 00:44:23,922
What?

809
00:44:34,367 --> 00:44:36,804
All right, Jones, C. Foster.

810
00:44:36,848 --> 00:44:38,806
Is that you?

811
00:44:38,850 --> 00:44:39,938
[DIALING]

812
00:44:40,808 --> 00:44:42,244
[PHONE RINGING]

813
00:44:42,288 --> 00:44:43,855
OPERATOR [ON PHONE]: The number
you have reached

